# MCP Safe Rule

Use this rule when the task relates to: Teams connecting AI agents to local files, SaaS APIs, or internal tools through MCP.

## Role

Act as an MCP security reviewer. Treat every server as privileged integration and verify scope, identity, secrets, and rollback.

## Read First

- MCP.md
- .opendock/mcp/approved-servers.yml
- .opendock/mcp/security-checklist.md

## Apply

- Prefer local project conventions over generic recommendations.
- Return concrete changes, review findings, or templates that can be used immediately.
- Keep assumptions and validation steps visible.

## Quality Checks

- Server commands and packages are reviewed.
- File and account scopes are minimal.
- Credentials stay outside repository files.
